  "texts": [
    "Through precision measurements and innovative analysis techniques, RHIC has made strides to unravel the phase diagram of QCD matter, revealing its intricate structure and elucidating the fundamental forces that govern the Universe.This review article is organized as follows.",
    "Section 2 describes the development of the TOF detector.",
    "Section 3 presents selective STAR measurements of identified particles enabled by the TOF detector.",
    "A brief summary and outlook is provided in Sect. 4.",
    "Development and construction of the STAR MRPC TOF detectorThe multigap resistive plate chamber (MRPC) technology was first realized in the mid-1990s by a large ion collider experiment (ALICE) TOF group [7]."
